Principle of Data visulation :
-Principle 1 -> Clarity
1.Avoid clutter
2.Use clear visual hierachies 

-Principle 2 ->Accessibility
1.Use color scheme that are color blind friendly
2.Ensure text is readable

-Principle 3 -> Accuracy
1.Use appropriate scales and axes
2.Avoid misleading representationes

-Principle 4 ->Relevance 
1.Tailor visulations to the audience
2.Highlight what's most important 

-Principle 5 ->Aesthelics 
1.Balance color and design element 
2.Use whitespace effectively 

-Principle 6 ->Interaction
1.Example of interaction tools(eg: hover, drill-down)
2.Benefitd of interaction is exploring data

-Principle 70 -> Context
1. Keep the big picture in mind
2. Compare and contrast data pointer
